verses.text: It \w is|strong="H3117"\w* \w a|strong="H3117"\w* good thing \w to|strong="H3117"\w* give praise \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H3117"\w* Lord, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w to|strong="H3117"\w* make melody \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w your|strong="H3117"\w* name, O Most High;
